headline: Exploring Analyst Estimates for Autodesk (ADSK) Q4 Earnings, Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Besides Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimates for Autodesk (ADSK), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended January 2025.
